{"tid":623641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[邊位巴打]啓德花園商場檔口失竊　600個胸圍被偷","createTime":"2018-04-10T07:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T07:25:24.000Z","uid":128993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84d4ef88a96b744b6a80735a4bcb55e596d50d59","tid":623641,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"黃大仙發生盜竊案。早上8時許，女負責人返回彩虹道121號啟德花園商場的攤檔準備時，發現攤檔有搜掠痕迹，經點算後證實損失約600個胸圍，約值約1.2萬元，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，翻查閉路電視片段了解，不排除賊人趁晚上無人經過時犯案。遇竊攤檔位於24小時開放的商場通道旁，並無防盜措施，事後照常營業。據了解，該攤檔上周亦曾遇竊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180410/s00001/1523338199116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180410%2Fs00001%2F1523338199116&d=14dy5Za6T0yLZEhG0Vyge%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=04e838ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180410%2Fs00001%2F1523338199116&h=89478c2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180410/s00001/1523338199116</a><br />\n<br />\n邊位巴打，出來認左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6253b5de572b77e5c77e069af7badd6645b61d4a","tid":623641,"uid":6644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"一個廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52da2bb37b829dc59c23b1cf93a1a98f1febf5a1","tid":623641,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.moegirl.org/common/4/45/%E6%88%91%E5%85%A8%E9%83%BD%E8%A6%81.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.moegirl.org%2Fcommon%2F4%2F45%2F%25E6